divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving to a church to do the air conditioning service when i noticed this object moving slowly over the trees. At first i thought it was a blimb of some kind but it had nothing hanging under it as blimbs do. I shot these pics and saved them to my computer but was in dought of what to do with them.
Summary: I noticed this moving over the trees slowly
